channel.description:
WarLeaks aims to provide a non political unbiased stance on military videos, war and combat footages from all around the world. Mainstream media can bring you only so far, but our aim is to provide the viewers a first hand experience on what happens around the world.

This way the viewer can form his/her own opinion on something you hear daily on the news but without a biased twist but rather from a independent source.

WarLeaks does not glorify war or violence in any case, WarLeaks can be seen a war archive and should be also seen as educational documentary channel. The purposes include news reporting, educating and giving the viewer a first hand experience of the tragic battles and combats that happen daily around the world.

Subscribe now to keep updated and to view first hand military videos, war and combat footage's and much more.

This channel is in no way affiliated with any Government, DND or DoD.
channel.title: WarLeaks - Military Videos & Combat Footage
